data.text:
Peter Bennett-Jones CBE (born 1955) is a British TV producer and agent, best known for series like Mr. Bean, Harry Enfield and The Vicar of Dibley.

In 1994-1997 he worked on both series of Harry Enfield and Chums. In 2000 he worked on the film Kevin & Perry Go Large.
